          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Returning Worker Accountability Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill exempts from the nonimmigrant H-2B visa (temporary nonagricultural services) annual numerical limitation for a fiscal year a returning worker who has already been counted toward such limitation during any of the preceding three fiscal years. </p> </p>]]></text>
